actions.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.
Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.
On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.
Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

official_title: A concurrent resolution providing for a conditional recess or adjournment of the Senate from Friday, April 10, 1992, or Saturday, April 11, 1992, until Tuesday, April 28, 1992, and an adjournment of the House on the legislative day of Thursday, April 9, 1992, until Tuesday, April 28, 1992.

summary.text: Provides for a recess or adjournment of the Senate from April 10 or 11 until April 28, 1992, and an adjournment of the House of Representatives from April 9 until April 28, 1992.
